<Font|titleFont>JOYSTICK<Font|helpFont><p><p>

<Font|smallBoldFont>Action				
		Joystick<Font|smallFont><p>
Pitch down					Stick forward<p>
Pitch up						Stick back<p>
Turn left						Stick left<p>
Turn right					Stick right<p>
Fire weapon					Button 1<p>
Fire missile					Button 2<p>
Fire boosters				Button 3 (hold)<p>
Drop chaff					Button 4<p>
Toggle directional lock	Button 5<p>
Point of view				Hatswitch<p><p>

<Font|smallBoldFont>To remap a joystick control<Font|smallFont><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpimg1|On the Allegiance main menu, click
<Font|smallBoldFont>Options.<Font|smallFont>><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|-or-><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|Any time during gameplay, press ESC, G, C.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpimg2|Double-click the action you want to reconfigure.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|-or-><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|Click the action you want to reconfigure, and then
press ENTER.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpimg3|To assign the action to a joystick control, press the
desired joystick button or move the joystick in the direction you
want.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|If the control you selected is already
mapped to another action and you
decide you don't want to change it, press ESC. If you do want to change
the control anyway, press ENTER, but then be sure you assign the other
action with a new control.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|To remove a mapping entirely from an action, press
DELETE.><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpimg4|To save your change(s), click
<Font|smallBoldFont>Accept.<Font|smallFont>><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|-or-><p><p>

<Bullet|hlpblank|To cancel your change(s) and keep all the previous
mappings, click <Font|smallBoldFont>Reject.<Font|smallFont>><p><p>

Note that if you want to reassign the hatswitch to another
action (for example, thrusting), click the Hat entry, and then
press ENTER to change the hatswitch focus to Hat as Buttons. Then
find the actions you want to assign to the hatswitch directions and change
as described above (in the thrusting example, assign each thrust direction
to a hatswitch direction).<p><p>

At any time, you can click <Font|smallBoldFont>Restore Defaults<Font|smallFont>
to return all control mappings to their original settings.
